	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ive seen alot of people saying that with a good connection and skills you can twist 5 songs and not lose any effects id just like to clear up this is NOT TRUE. The max you can do is 4 (mathmatically) and even that requires that you exploit the bug that allows a song to finish even if you cancel it and start a new one before it completes (for example before you get the "your wounds begin to heal" message you cancel hymn and begin singing selos for example.) Perhaps with an INSANE connection you can make the drop so short that it wont be noticed (while twisting 5) however if you do that you risk enacting the stripping bug (if a song lands at the exact moment the last cycle of it has fallen, this will happen, Song falls Song lands Song falls... all at once) Anyways id just like to clear that up. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
