	   <tr><td colspan=2>&gt;magic chant (27 base 1.15 for drm effect) = 31.5 per tick = 187 a minute. <br>&gt;fire chant (45 base 1.15 for drm effect) = 51.4 <br>&gt;per tick = 307 a minute. <br>&gt;<br>&gt;cold chant.. same as fire <br>&gt;<br>&gt;So a minute at level 46(if the mobs are rooted) thats 800 damage mana free. <br><br>Well, 1 minor correction.  A tick = 6 seconds (not 10 seconds which is what you<br>used for your numbers).  This makes the damage with the MM Drum<br>magic chant = 31.5 or 315 a minute<br>fire chant     = 51.4 or 514 a minute<br>cold same as fire<br><br>So a minute at level 46 (if the mobs are rooted) that's  1343 damage.  I usually just<br>explain it to others (I'm using the Tambourine rather than the drums and the levels<br>are slightly off) that I can do about 500 damage every 20 seconds (a minute is a<br>LONG time in a fight).<br><br>Mahew, Clan Ravenheart<br>51 Minstrel, Xev<br>&nbsp;<br>Mahew Ravenheart<br>51 Minstrel, Xev</td></tr>
